Applozic,s,chat,messaging,sdk,and,api,toolkit,allows,businesses,to,integrate,messaging,into,apps,without,building,a,new,infrastructure,The,Applozic,API,is,RESTful,uses,HTTP,methods,over,SSL,and,supports,JSON,data,types,Use,the,API,to,send,messages,get,a,list,of,messages,sent,to,a,user,delete,a,message,or,delete,a,conversation,thread,See,the,API,documentation,for,detailed,method,descriptions,and,instructions,on,getting,started,with,Applozic